Package be.uantwerpen.fti.ei.interfaces

Interface IFactory

All Known Implementing Classes:
J2DAFactory, J2DIFactory, J2DPFactory
public interface IFactory
Base factory interface that must be inherited by other factory classes
An interface to define all base entity creation and package related system methods
